There is still autocorrelation. I decided to use the lag as regressor in the model.

In [ ]:
lag = 1
df["lag"] = df["TP AKONUTSAT4 TOPLAM"].shift(lag)
df = df.drop(df.head(lag).index) # Remove First month data
